---

<ProductLayout {title} heading="Conservatories & Orangeries" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>A lot of conservatories these days have that mass-produced look. We do things differently, building classical Victorian designs in hardwood that you won't see anywhere else. A bespoke oak-framed conservatory or orangery that suits your home and the way you live in it.</p>

    <p>A timber frame might cost a bit more to begin with, but there's less upkeep and it does far more for the look of your home. Every job is built to your requirements, so you end up with something a cut above the average conservatory or orangery.</p>

    <p>To discuss our full range of conservatories and orangeries, please contact us on <strong>01228 512303</strong> or visit our joinery showroom in Brisco, Carlisle, Cumbria.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Classical Victorian conservatories and orangeries</li>
      <li>Luxury oak-framed garden rooms</li>
      <li>Designs that perfectly complement your home's architecture</li>
      <li>Low-maintenance, high-quality hardwood constructions</li>
      <li>Tailored solutions to suit your lifestyle and space</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>
